-- Santander Sells Loan Recovery Unit to Lindorff, Expansion Says
-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 2012-03-06T06:47:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-06/santander-sells-loan-recovery-unit-to-lindorff-expansion-says.html
Banco Santander SA (SAN)  completed the
sale of its loan recovery unit to Lindorff AS,  Expansion  said,
citing David Perez, head of the Norwegian company’s Spanish
unit.  The price of the deal wasn’t disclosed, the newspaper said.  Click here for web link  To contact the reporters on this story:
